sources.title: The Big Cat
sources.description: 1949 directed by Phil Karlson starring Preston Foster, Lon McAllister, Forrest Tucker, Peggy Ann Garner, Irving Bacon, Sara Haden, Skip Homeier and Gene Reynolds. Set during the Great Depression, a young man goes into the high country where his mother was born in hopes of finding work. What he discovers are bitter resentments and a land plagued with drought. This copy has been sharpened a bit
